name: Playing in the Jellyfish Rift
description: “The Jellyfish rift is the migration path of some cosmic fauna. Jellyfish uses it to cross dimensions, but some are caught to be played with, just like squishy balls of light”.  This is a digitally developed art originally painted on its negative colors on paper using watercolor technique. This limited edition of the reveled piece is 4377x3318 px, 6.4 MB, painted in 140lb cold pressed cotton paper (8.6x9 inches) by Art Matioli.
